218822.title: Scarlett Road, looking north, from south of East Drive
218822.text:
[ca. 1970]
Description: 1 photonegative : b&w; ; 11 x 13 cm
Citation: Fonds 1257, Series 1057, Item 8007
Condition: Vinegar syndrome has affected the original film media. It has been frozen for preservation reasons, and therefore may not be requested for viewing in the Research Hall. 
Copyright: Copyright was transferred to the City of Toronto by the copyright owner. ...more
Scope: Item consists of one photonegative. The Queensbury House hotel is on west side, at 250 Scarlett Road.
